to help kids with ADHD,

16
00:00:46,846 --> 00:00:49,614
anxiety,
obsessive-compulsive disorder,

17
00:00:49,615 --> 00:00:54,519
migraines,
Tourette's and more.

18
00:00:54,520 --> 00:00:57,722
This study is not
about technology.

19
00:00:57,723 --> 00:01:00,792
The MRI machine behind me
may look impressive,

20
