22
00:01:04,629 --> 00:01:06,631
What this study
is really about

23
00:01:06,632 --> 00:01:09,634
is faith in science.

24
00:01:09,635 --> 00:01:19,377
It's about the power
of thoughts to heal.

25
00:01:19,378 --> 00:01:24,883
All you need is the power
of suggestion.

26
00:01:24,884 --> 00:01:37,762
[theme music playing]

27
00:01:37,763 --> 00:01:40,865
A placebo is something
that shouldn't work,

28
00:01:40,866 --> 00:01:43,168
but due to the power
of suggestion

29
00:01:43,169 --> 00:01:46,571
and because of the strength
of our belief, does.

30
00:01:46,572 --> 00:01:49,707
But we don't fully understand
yet how they work.

31
00:01:49,708 --> 00:01:52,477
 There could be
 an evolutionary explanation.

32
00:01:52,478 --> 00:01:55,213
 For example, if a small child
 hurts themselves,

33
00:01:55,214 --> 00:01:58,750
 negative symptoms like pain
 and crying can be good.

34
00:01:58,751 --> 00:02:01,519
 They keep the child safe
 and still

35
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:03,688
 while signaling adults
 to come help.

36
00:02:03,689 --> 00:02:05,223
 When help arrives,

37
00:02:05,224 --> 00:02:07,458
 even if it
 has no active effect,

38
00:02:07,459 --> 00:02:08,826
 the child's brain may feel

39
00:02:08,827 --> 00:02:11,262
 it has permission to redirect

40
00:02:11,263 --> 00:02:13,298
 resources away
 from seeking help

41
00:02:13,299 --> 00:02:15,667
 and onto actually healing.

42
00:02:15,668 --> 00:02:18,570
 Modern medicine has found
 a way to harness this power

43
00:02:18,571 --> 00:02:20,905
 by prescribing placebos.

44
00:02:20,906 --> 00:02:23,508
But not all placebos work
the same.

45
00:02:23,509 --> 00:02:26,477
For example, a sugar pill
will help your headache more

46
00:02:26,478 --> 00:02:28,246
if given to you by a doctor

47
00:02:28,247 --> 00:02:29,881
than by a poker buddy.

48
00:02:29,882 --> 00:02:32,984
And the color
of the placebo matters, too.

49
00:02:32,985 --> 00:02:36,287
A blue pill will work
to make you feel calm

50
00:02:36,288 --> 00:02:37,889
better than a white pill

51
00:02:37,890 --> 00:02:40,692
because blue
is a more calming color.

52
00:02:40,693 --> 00:02:43,294
And a red pill
will keep you awake

53
00:02:43,295 --> 00:02:44,596
and give you more energy

54
00:02:44,597 --> 00:02:46,464
than a blue pill will.

55
00:02:46,465 --> 00:02:48,900
A capsule will work
better than a pill

56
00:02:48,901 --> 00:02:56,274
because it looks
more important.

57
00:02:56,275 --> 00:03:00,278
Also, an injection will work
better than a capsule

58
00:03:00,279 --> 00:03:02,614
because it seems
more serious

59
00:03:02,615 --> 00:03:04,482
and potent.

60
00:03:04,483 --> 00:03:07,285
There's even evidence
that fake or sham surgeries

61
00:03:07,286 --> 00:03:08,786
have positive effects.

62
00:03:08,787 --> 00:03:10,521
It may be fake medicine,

63
00:03:10,522 --> 00:03:12,523
